data.title: CONTENTdm
data.meta_description: President Calvin Coolidge has a lawn party on his 55th birthday and receives a cake from his neighbors. Mrs. Grace Coolidge filming activities with motion picture camera. Various scenes of the Terry, Montana Cowboy Band playing. The Coolidges walk onto grounds of the State Game Lodge, Mrs. Coolidge receives bouquet from child, Mr. Coolidge receives and models a pair of chaps. Various scenes of Coolidges in receiving line. Coolidges reviewing mounted Boy Scout Troop.
